The same thing happened to me. See?

821
01:28:03,489 --> 01:28:05,615
I wasn't lying. See?

822
01:28:05,699 --> 01:28:07,616
Fuck this shit!

823
01:29:15,513 --> 01:29:17,347
No!

824
01:29:19,392 --> 01:29:21,185
