825
01:29:21,269 --> 01:29:23,479
-There must be a way out of this.
-Shut up!

826
01:29:23,562 --> 01:29:27,148
Just shut up! My family needs me!

827
01:29:28,567 --> 01:29:30,985
No! God!

828
01:29:31,069 --> 01:29:33,070
God! No!

829
01:29:33,155 --> 01:29:34,572
