It's a mistake I'd like to fix.

832
01:29:50,795 --> 01:29:53,380
I'm gonna kill you, you sick asshole.

833
01:29:55,342 --> 01:29:56,467
Lawrence!

834
01:29:57,552 --> 01:29:58,844
Stop it.

835
01:30:03,390 --> 01:30:05,391
Lawrence, just calm down.

836
01:30:05,476 --> 01:30:08,102
There's a way out of here.
There's a way out!

837
01:30:08,187 --> 01:30:09,062
Lawrence!

838
01:30:11,148 --> 01:30:13,149
No! What are you... No!

839
01:30:13,233 --> 01:30:15,776
Oh, my God! Lawrence!

840
01:30:17,737 --> 01:30:20,155
What are you doing?

841
01:31:31,930 --> 01:31:33,973
