-You have to die.
-No! I want to live!

849
01:32:17,523 --> 01:32:19,524
-I'm sorry.
-I want to live!

850
01:32:19,609 --> 01:32:21,943
-My family...
-Argh!

851
01:32:35,456 --> 01:32:38,249
There! I've done it!

852
01:32:39,376 --> 01:32:41,419
Now show them to me!

853
01:32:44,799 --> 01:32:46,841
Show them to me.

854
01:32:46,926 --> 01:32:49,219
-Thank you very much, Officer.
-Larry?

855
01:32:49,302 --> 01:32:51,303
Did you get through to him?

856
01:32:51,387 --> 01:32:53,889
-There's still no answer.
-I've called the police.

857
01:32:53,973 --> 01:32:56,016
Everything is OK.

858
01:33:11,448 --> 01:33:13,032
You bastard!

859
01:33:13,116 --> 01:33:16,285
I'll fucking kill you! I'll fucking kill you!

860
01:33:16,369 --> 01:33:18,370
You fucking bastard!

861
01:33:18,454 --> 01:33:22,123
I'll fucking kill you!
You fucking bastard!

862
01:33:22,208 --> 01:33:24,334
I'll fucking kill you!

863
01:33:24,418 --> 01:33:25,961
I'll fucking kill you.

864
