870
01:34:33,157 --> 01:34:35,575
Don't leave me!

871
01:34:35,659 --> 01:34:36,951
No!

872
01:34:37,036 --> 01:34:39,078
No! No!

873
01:34:41,040 --> 01:34:43,082
No! Ow!

874
01:34:45,383 --> 01:34:49,082
Lawrence! Lawrence!

875
01:34:53,008 --> 01:34:54,425
D-Don't worry.

876
01:34:54,510 --> 01:34:56,010
I'll bring someone back.

877
01:34:56,095 --> 01:34:57,720
I promise.

878
01:35:18,183 --> 01:35:20,226
Key.

879
01:35:38,451 --> 01:35:40,494
Key. Key!

880
01:36:02,806 --> 01:36:05,725
Hello, Mr. Hindle.

881
01:36:05,809 --> 01:36:08,186
Or as they called you around the hospital...

882
01:36:09,271 --> 01:36:10,313
