886
01:36:23,493 --> 01:36:25,994
Will you murder a mother and her child

887
01:36:26,079 --> 01:36:28,455
to save yourself?

888
01:36:28,538 --> 01:36:30,498
Dr. Gordon's time is up.

889
01:36:30,582 --> 01:36:31,832
Mrs. Gordon!

890
01:36:32,709 --> 01:36:36,003
Listen carefully, if you will. There are rules.

891
01:36:36,087 --> 01:36:38,506
