to his own sicko games.

898
01:37:55,995 --> 01:37:59,872
Hello, Mark, Paul, Amanda,
Zep, Adam, Dr. Gordon.

899
01:37:59,956 --> 01:38:01,665
I want to play a game.

900
01:38:27,898 --> 01:38:31,443
